Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["SymmetryAdaptedBasis", "Section",
 PageWidth:>WindowWidth,
 Evaluatable->False,
 InitializationCell->True,
 InitializationGroup->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.42968234673812*^9, 3.429682350151795*^9}, {
  3.8432919854658713`*^9, 3.843292014201957*^9}},
 AspectRatioFixed->
  True,ExpressionUUID->"e9ed4993-16c1-4bd0-9652-f398499c894e"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"SymmetryAdaptedBasis", "::", "usage"}], " ", "=", 
   "\"\<SymmetryAdaptedBasis constructs a symmetry-adapted basis of spin \
states. \n\nThe syntax SymmetryAdaptedBasis[spinsys, {\\\"GroupName\\\", n}, \
opts] may be used for exact calculations, where \\\"GroupName\\\" refers to \
the name of the group as a string, and n refers to the order of the group. \
Exact calculations are currently only supported for {\\\"SymmetricGroup\\\", \
\\\"CyclicGroup\\\"}. For example, the command \
SymmetryAdaptedBasis[{{1,1/2},{2,1/2},{3,1/2}}, {\\\"SymmetricGroup\\\", 3}, \
opts] defines a symmetry-adapted basis for three-spin-1/2 particles with \
respect to the group \!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(S\), \(3\)]\). \n\nFor arbitraty \
permutation groups the syntax SymmetryAdaptedBasis[spinsys, {{\\\"GroupName\\\
\", n}, {\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(p\), \(1\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(p\), \
\(2\)]\),...}},] may be used for numerical calculations. Here, the set \
{\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(p\), \(1\)]\),\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(p\), \(2\)]\),...} \
represents the corresponding group elements in the form of SpinDynamica spin \
permutation operators. For example, the command \
SymmetryAdaptedBasis[{{1,1/2},{2,1/2}}, {{\\\"AlternatingGroup\\\", \
2},{SpinPermutationOperator[{}],SpinPermutationOperator[{1,2}]}}] defines a \
symmetry-adapted basis for two-spin-1/2 particles with respect to the group \
\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(A\), \(2\)]\).\n\nIf the spin system specifications are \
omitted SymmetryAdaptedBasis will try to work with the currently active spin \
system.\>\""}], ";"}]], "Input",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5470255141898823`*^9, 3.547025521675369*^9}, {
   3.843292017931348*^9, 3.843292023521279*^9}, {3.843299657828489*^9, 
   3.843299672704005*^9}, {3.8432997440167236`*^9, 3.843300080107231*^9}, {
   3.843300138477498*^9, 3.843300184109269*^9}, {3.843544877626382*^9, 
   3.8435448926293387`*^9}, {3.84373011736066*^9, 3.843730522037243*^9}, 
   3.8522936208915267`*^9, {3.892013272443365*^9, 3.8920132886393905`*^9}, {
   3.892013330964425*^9, 3.892013369017071*^9}, {3.892014107175629*^9, 
